{
  "stem": "21308.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You'd go into a hut and people were obviously very pleased to see you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I felt sorry for the Norwegians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because Norway wasn't free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they were, in fact, the first people to go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I got a message to say that Swedish Red Cross column was coming in to take them home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so, that was the end of my help with the sealing off the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I gave the boss of the Norwegians, Andreas Orgens, a bottle of whisky.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I autographed the label.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I said, now, there you are.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You-- this is the real McCoy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is Scotch whisky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Ration it out very carefully.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But keep the empty bottle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because I will come to Norway one day and I shall hope I'll see you and the empty bottle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Anyway, I went about-- 9, 10 years later, I went on winter maneuvers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I called on him and his family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the little boy who had been born since his dad got home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And Andreas said to me, I've got something I want to show you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he produced this empty bottle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he said, I've looked after it very carefully.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now I have great pleasure in giving it to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't want it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You keep it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I said, it's empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It's no good to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But then, of course, at the end of it all, at the end of it, when we were told we were coming home, we had a big parade in the sports ground.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I can show you photographs of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then we eventually handed over to a commando.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And what happened, I just don't know, except what I wrote in my story.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
